name: Love, Death & Buddha
description: They see dragon, angel face, skull, lotus and meditator in this painting. I see nothing, but I feel all. Love, Death & Buddha is part of my Astral Projection Toolkit series, I use image like this to get in the zone.  Artist: UGLYKIKI(Kiki Wu). Created in April, 2021. Dimension: 2880 x 1620px.
